      "writtenOn": "2015-09-17T23:20:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m confused.  can\u0027t prebuilts be used in place?\nlldb prebuilts are.\n\nhttps://android.googlesource.com/platform/manifest/+/lldb-master-dev/default.xml\n\nJust checkout \u0026 build\n\ncan\u0027t both of these scripts just depend on a script to copy prebuilts?",
